author: Adam Jeffery
title: Photos show patients arriving at the Javits Center field hospital in New York City
description: In just over a week, The Jacob K. Javits Center has been transformed into a field hospital operated by the U.S. National Guard and has started to take in coronavirus patients to help alleviate the stress on existing hospital systems.
content:
